WEBVTT

00:00.429 --> 00:02.405
Introducing AirPods Max.

00:04.157 --> 00:08.335
Every aspect has been designed for uncompromising fit and performance.

00:09.013 --> 00:13.305
Machined aluminum ear cups connect by a unique suspension system,...

00:13.449 --> 00:17.949
...enabling independent articulation to the telescoping arms of the headband.

00:18.955 --> 00:23.506
This flexes to fit a wide range of head sizes, with a warp-knit canopy...

00:23.689 --> 00:27.761
...maximizing comfort and breathability while an acoustically optimized...

00:27.873 --> 00:31.315
...knit seamlessly surrounds the magnetically attached cushions.

00:32.326 --> 00:36.131
These components work in harmony to maintain an exceptional over-ear seal;...

00:36.403 --> 00:38.667
...the foundation for its incredible sound.

00:40.348 --> 00:43.090
Custom drivers deliver high-fidelity playback...

00:43.188 --> 00:46.422
...with ultra low distortion across the entire audible range.

00:47.078 --> 00:49.732
And a pair of Apple-designed H1 chips allow...

00:49.807 --> 00:53.363
...computational audio features like Adaptive EQ,...

00:53.502 --> 00:56.309
...which tailors sound to your bespoke fit by measuring...

00:56.384 --> 01:00.067
...and then adjusting what you're hearing up to 200 times per second.

01:00.829 --> 01:03.689
Active Noise Cancellation uses eight microphones...

01:03.745 --> 01:06.676
...positioned to sense and block noise from any direction.

01:07.063 --> 01:11.288
A single button press activates Transparency mode, letting you hear what's around you.

01:17.185 --> 01:21.093
And spatial audio, which utilizes accelerometers and gyroscopes...

01:21.177 --> 01:24.632
...to track head movement for immersive, theater-like sound.

01:25.639 --> 01:29.609
And the Digital Crown allows precise control of volume and playback.

01:32.075 --> 01:36.703
With up to 20 hours of listening time, best-in-class Active Noise Cancellation,...

01:36.901 --> 01:42.959
...and magical experience, AirPods Max sets the new standard for over-ear headphones.

